rows.label: tlk43420171_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Sure is a good thing my
Blade's so powerful!

rows.label: tlk43420171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The other day my Blade
found a poor sod who'd
fallen onto Acedia's back.

rows.label: tlk43420171_02_msg0003
rows.name:
She was from the refugee camp,
said she didn't want any help
from a Blade. Got quite angry...

rows.label: tlk43420171_02_msg0004
rows.name:
But we couldn't just leave her
there like that, so we had to
manhandle her out of there!
